<DOCNO> AP891128-0190 </DOCNO>
<FILEID>AP-NR-11-28-89 0742EST</FILEID>
<FIRST>r f BC-Britain-Stocks     11-28 0082</FIRST>
<SECOND>BC-Britain-Stocks,0087</SECOND>
<HEAD>London Shares Higher at Midday</HEAD>
<HEAD>Eds: will be led after closing</HEAD>
<DATELINE>LONDON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Stock prices rose in early trading Tuesday.
   At 12:05 p.m. local time, the Financial Times-Stock Exchange
100-share index was up 19.3 points at 2,243.6.
   Midday volume totaled 271.2 million shares, up from 194 million
